From 04c7bf452228e5261877bde6c7fe21d9f9ac7d83 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Artem Goncharov <artem.goncharov@gmail.com>
Date: Fri, 28 Jun 2024 20:50:35 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 1006/1026] Add JsonSchema validation framework

A step towards generation of OpenAPI by inspecting service code is
decorating API methods with jsonschema validators (same as it is done in
Nova, Cinder, Manila). This adds following features:

- forced and strict request body validation
- validation of query parameters
- validation of the response body
- OpenAPI generation

Change-Id: I7b7d29c1de82aa0bcb332ad9f5c356346479ee37
(cherry picked from commit a1d3a275b9152f08a6c0e21d80e0b45337ac18de)
